latestPosts.caption:
Namma veetla ellarukum theriyum, moringa evlo powerful nu… athu ippo na use panra face wash layum iruku!
Moringa has 7 times more vitamin C than orange—and trust me, my skin feels the difference.

Deep-ah cleanse pannum, pigmentation-ah kuraikkum, but skin-ah dry pannadhu.
Raw milk-oda combo la moringa, skin-a soft-ah bright-aakudhu.

Just one use laye, I could see the glow.
Naan start panniten… unga turn eppo?

#NatHabit #FreshAyurveda #GlowWithMoringa #NaturalSkincare #breathelifeintoyourbeauty
